    "label": "FACIS Simulation \u2014 REST Snapshot API",
    "disabled": false,
    "info": "FACIS Simulation \u2014 REST Snapshot API\n\nRead-only GET endpoints that return the latest snapshot stored by the\nFeeds tab in flow context (`latest_meters`, `latest_pv`, `latest_weather`,\n`latest_price`, `latest_consumers`).\n\nEndpoints (preserved from src/api/rest/routes/):\n  GET /api/v1/health\n  GET /api/v1/meters\n  GET /api/v1/meters/:meter_id/current\n  GET /api/v1/pv\n  GET /api/v1/weather\n  GET /api/v1/prices\n  GET /api/v1/loads\n"
  },
